author: lundblad
msg: Don't initialize RA library in svnversion.
svnversion doesn't directly depend on libsvn_ra, so using symbols from it
causes link failures on some platforms.  svnversion doesn't actually
use the RA layer, so there is no need to initialize it.  Note that
calling svn_ra_initialize() isn't required anyway for compatibility
